            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1j0018-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-h0017a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:03:16.446+09:00">Explaining Graphs and Unravelling Characters</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-h0017a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:03:55.949+09:00">First [Part]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p0024a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:05:05.438+09:00">Thirty-one graphs newly added.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p0025a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T22:19:11.55+09:00">ONE is the opening Great Beginning. The Way is established in unity, and by way of creative innovation it divides into (the dyad of) Heaven and Earth, and it is then transmogrified to bring to completion all manner of creatures.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p0023a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:08:58.646+09:00"> </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p0025a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:13:30.889+09:00">The Minor Xu edition has "Great Extreme" for "Great Beginning".</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p0025a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:12:47.08+09:00">Quite generally everything that belongs under 一 is said to "follow ONE".</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p0025a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T22:57:46.288+09:00">[Pronunciation initial 於 rhyme 悉]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p0106a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:20:09.806+09:00">THREE, the Way of Heaven, Earth, and Man.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p10397a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:22:21.28+09:00">FOUR, the number of Yin. Resembles the shape of a fourfold division.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1j0018_tls_001-p9657a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-12-07T07:25:55.134+09:00">TWO is the number of Earth. Is formed from a pair of ONEs.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
